By Matthew Savides and Nathi OlifantThe deputy mayor of the Richmond municipality in KwaZulu-Natal was murdered on Sunday night. Thandazile Phoswa s slaying comes a month after the council s municipal manager S bu Sithole was gunned down in an apparent hit.While details are still sketchy TMG Digital has learnt that Phoswa s estranged boyfriend a bodyguard at the uMshwathi municipality handed himself over to police. Officers have seized the apparent murder weapon. The municipality is devastated. We have just lost a municipal manager a month ago. We hope the police do their work. We condemn this senseless murder regardless of who committed it said council spokesman Sibonelo Bhengu.